\c 133
\s Ukuthandana kwabazalwane
\d Ingoma yokwenyuka, ekaDavida
\p
\v 1 Khangela, kuhle kangakanani njalo kumnandi kangakanani ukuhlala kwabazalwane ndawonye ngitsho babe munye\x + Heb. 13.1.\x*.
\v 2 Kufanana lamafutha amahle\x + Eks. 30.25,30.\x* phezu kwekhanda\x + Eks. 29.7. Levi 8.12. Hlab. 23.5.\x*, ehlela endevini, indevu zikaAroni, ehlele emphethweni wezembatho zakhe\x + Eks. 28.32. 39.23. Jobe 30.18.\x*,
\v 3 njengamazolo eHermoni\x + Dute. 3.9.\x*, ehlela entabeni\x + Hlab. 87.1.\x* zeZiyoni\x + Dute. 4.48.\x*; ngoba lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* yalaya isibusiso, impilo kuze kube phakade\x + Levi 25.21. Dute. 28.8. Hlab. 42.8. 44.4. 68.28. 71.3.\x*.
